<!DOCTYPE html>

<html>
<head>
    <title>Notification on Ineligible for Attending the Examination @Model.ClassCode</title>
    <style type="text/css">
        html, body, p {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-size: 17px;
            font-family: MingLiU;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div>
        <p>Hello @Model.DisplayName,<br /></p>
        <p>
            @Model.CourseName <br />
            Notification on Ineligible for Attending the Examination @Model.ClassCode
        </p>
        <p>
            Please be informed that you have failed to fulfill the attendance requirement of captioned course and therefore ineligible for attending the examination to be held on @Model.Date.<br />
            Please find the attached notification for details.<br />
            Should you have enquiry, please contact us at telephone: 2100 900 or email: spdc@hkic.edu.hk<br />
            <br />
            Thank you.<br />

            School of Professional Development in Construction (SPDC)<br />
            Hong Kong Institute of Construction (HKIC)<br />
        </p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
